etch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK Semibold\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>三、 兌換規範與權益行使</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>兌換效力</strong>：積分可用於兌換「積分商城」內之指定實體商品、會員服務或虛擬權益。兌換訂單經系統確認後，相應積分將即時扣除。<strong>除因法律強制規定或本平台認可之特殊事由外，已扣除之積分不予返還。</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>時效性權益</strong>：如兌換標的屬會員服務或其他具時效性之權益，該服務自兌換成功時起自動開通。其具體使用期限、行使條件與限制規則，悉依該項權益之專屬說明頁面為準。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK Semibold\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>四、 權利聲明與變更</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>計畫調整</strong>：本平台保留在事先於平台內公告之情況下，調整積分商城商品種類、兌換價值、兌換門檻，以及暫停或終止積分計畫之權利。</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>條款修訂</strong>：本協議內容及積分獲取規則之最終解釋權，或相關爭議之認定，均由 <strong>LUMO GUIDE（路盟）</strong>依相關法律法規及誠信原則處理。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 17px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong>Points Usage and Service Terms</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>1. Legal Nature and Restrictions</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Definition and Nature</strong>: Points issued by this application (hereinafter referred to as \"the Platform\") constitute virtual rewards for user engagement. Points are intended solely for internal use within the Platform and do not possess any monetary value or characteristic of legal tender.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Prohibited Actions</strong>: Points are non-transferable and are restricted to the original account of issuance. Users are strictly prohibited from <strong>transferring, pledging, gifting, or inheriting</strong> points. Points shall not be exchanged for cash, redeemed for currency, or be eligible for refunds. The Platform reserves the right to confiscate points involved in unauthorized third-party transactions.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>2. Acquisition of Points</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\">Users may earn points by completing the actions specified in the table below, subject to the rules in effect at the time of the activity. The Platform reserves the right to adjust the methods, ratios, and details of point acquisition at its sole discretion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15.9px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><span style=\"font