nt-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang HK\'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; min-height: 17px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>3. Redemption and Exercise of Rights</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Finality of Redemption</strong>: Points may be used in the \"Point Mall\" to redeem designated physical goods, membership services, or other virtual rights. Upon confirmation of a redemption order, the corresponding points will be automatically deducted. <strong>Points are non-refundable once deducted</strong>, except as required by law or approved by the Platform under exceptional circumstances.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Time-Sensitive Rights</strong>: For redemptions involving membership services or other time-limited rights, the service shall be activated automatically upon successful redemption. Specific terms, conditions, and expiration dates shall be governed by the specific rules of said rights.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>4. General Provisions and Amendments</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Program Modification</strong>: The Platform reserves the right to adjust the types of goods/services in the Point Mall, modify redemption values, or suspend/terminate the Points Program, provided that prior notice is given within the Platform.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;\"><strong>Final Interpretation</strong>: The right of final interpretation regarding these terms and the determination of any disputes related to points shall be vested in <strong>LUMO GUIDE</strong></li>\r\n</ol>','2025-07-24 17:07:29','2026-03-02 20:16:52'),(5,'企業經營類型',5,'business_type','[\"\\u9910\\u5ef3\",\"\\u4f4f\\u5bbf\",\"\\u7968\\u52d9\",\"\\u8cfc\\u7269\",\"\\u666f\\u9ede\"]','2025-07-25 10:39:09','2025-09-20 05:37:59'),(6,'掌握語言',5,'languages','[\"\\u4e2d\\u6587\",\"English\",\"\\u6cd5\\u8a9e(Fran\\u00e7ais)\",\"\\u5fb7\\u8a9e(Deutsch)\",\"\\u7fa9\\u5927\\u5229\\u8a9e(Italiano)\",\"\\u897f\\u73ed\\u7259\\u8a9e(Espa\\u00f1ol)\",\"\\u7ca4\\u8bed(\\u5ee3\\u6771\\u8a71)\",\"\\u65e5\\u8a9e(\\u65e5\\u672c\\u8a9e)\",\"\\u97d3\\u8a9e(\\ud55c\\uad6d\\uc778)\",\"\\u99ac\\u4f86\\u8a9e(Bahasa Melayu)\",\"\\u571f\\u8033\\u5176\\u8a9e(T\\u00fcrk\\u00e7e)\",\"\\u514b\\u7f85\\u5730\\u4e9e\\u8a9e(Hrvatski)\",\"\\u6377\\u514b\\u8a9e(\\u010de\\u0161tina)\",\"\\u5308\\u7259\\u5229\\u8a9e\\uff08Magyar\\uff09\",\"\\u745e\\u5178\\u8a9e\",\"\\u6cf0\\u8a9e\",\"\\u963f\\u62c9\\u4f2f\\u8a9e\",\"\\u65af\\u6d1b\\u4f10\\u514b\\u8bed\"]','2025-07-25 11:26:43','2025-12-21 01:23:09'),(7,'導遊類型',5,'guide_type','[\"Local guide\",\"Driver guide\",\"Tour leader\",\"Travel agency\",\"Other\"]','2025-07-25 11:29:26','2025-07-25 11:29:26'),(8,'導遊會員權益',4,'vip_guide_ability','發佈城市\r\n在線預約各城市的導游和商家\r\n與同行和商家在線聊天\r\n發佈景點、資訊、交通、設施、活動的權利\r\n評價景點、資訊、交通、設施、活動的權利\r\n積分兌换權利\r\n邀請同行或商家持續獲得積分','2025-08-10 03:20:07','2025-11-18 02:39:23'),(9,'企業會員權益',4,'vip_company_ability','Regular||可添加一個展示店鋪||在線即時聊天||在線預訂，預約管理||城市內容中的推薦為期三天||積分兌換||邀請好友持續累積積\r\nGold|| 享有Regular所有功能和權限||可添加同類型下多個商鋪||城市內容中的推薦二十天||平台內首頁列表推薦五天 ||店鋪展示\r\nDiamond||享有Gold會員所有功能和權限||可添加不同類型下多個商鋪||平台內首頁大圖輪播推薦五天||平台內首頁大圖輪播推薦後再列表推薦十五天','2025-08-10 03:21:22','2025-11-18 00:39:44'),(10,'邀請說明',4,'invite_rule','邀請會員類型	相應積分 (單位：FUN)	備註說明\r\n邀請商家： 288	需依平台審核通過為準，須通過資質認證；商家用戶每一次續費，您將再次獲得相應積分（多次積分獎勵）。\r\n\r\n邀請旅遊從業者：166	需依平台審核通過為準，須通過資質認證；旅遊從業用戶每一次續費，您將再次獲得相應積分（多次積分獎勵）。\r\n\r\n邀請成功 (一般用戶)：30	受邀者需完成註冊（一次性積分獎勵）。','2025-08-11 18:34:58','2026-03-01 06:33:24'),(11,'VIP會員服務付款協議',2,'vip_user_protocol','<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>路盟 Lumo Guide 應用程式 VIP 會員服務付款協議</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>生效日期：2025年10月1日</strong><br /><strong>最後更新日期：2025年10月1日</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">歡迎使用 路盟 Lumo Guide（以下稱「本應用程式」）。本協議是您（以下稱「用戶」）與本應用程式營運者之間具有法律約束力的協議。請仔細閱讀本協議，其說明了我們如何收集、使用、儲存及保護您的個人資料，並明確規定了雙方，特別是關於網絡支付的權利與義務。若您不同意本協議的任何內容，請立即停止使用本應用程式。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>一、 協議的接受與修改</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">當您下載、安裝、註冊、存取或使用本應用程式時，即表示您已閱讀、理解、並同意接受本協議的所有條款與條件，並承諾遵守所有適用的法律與法規。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們有權根據業務發展需要或為符合奧地利及歐盟法律要求而單方面修改本協議。修改後的協議將於本應用程式內公布更新版本，並註明最後更新日期。若您於協議修改後繼續使用本應用程式，即視為接受修改後的協議。對於重大變更，我們將盡合理努力提供更明確的通知。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>二、 帳號註冊與使用</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您需提供真實、準確、最新及完整的資料進行註冊，並有義務及時更新此等資料。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您須對您的帳號及密碼負有保密責任，並對在您帳號下發生的所有活動承擔法律責任。一旦發現任何未經授權使用您帳號的情況，應立即通知我們。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您不得利用本應用程式從事任何非法、侵權或違反公序良俗的行為，否則我們有權立即暫停或終止您的帳號，並保留追究法律責任的權利。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>三、 隱私權與資料保護</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們將依照單獨的《隱私權政策》以及《奧地利資料保護法》和歐盟《通用資料保護條例》的規定，合法、合理、必要地收集、處理、使用及保護您的個人資料。該《隱私權政策》為本協議不可分割的一部分。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們可能收集的資料包括但不限於：姓名、電子郵件地址、位置資訊、裝置識別碼、支付相關資訊及服務使用紀錄。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">關於您的資料主體權利（如存取、更正、刪除、限制處理、資料可攜性及反對權），請參閱我們的《隱私權政策》並透過指定聯絡方式提出請求。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>四、 服務內容</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">Lumo Guide 提供導覽、路線規劃、景點推薦及相關增值服務（以下統稱「本服務」）。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們保留隨時修改、暫停或終止部分或全部服務的權利，恕不另行個別通知。若法律要求，對於服務的重大變更或終止，我們將提供提前通知。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>五、 網絡支付條款</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>支付方式</strong><br />本應用程式支援以下支付方式：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">信用卡/借记卡</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">第三方支付平台（如：Apple Pay、Google Pay、PayPal等）</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">其他本應用程式另行公告之支付方式。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>支付授權與合同成立</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">當您進行支付操作時，即表示您發出具有約束力的要約，授權我們或我們合作的第三方支付服務提供商從您指定的支付方式中扣除相應款項。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">合同在我們無條件接受您的要約並透過系統或電郵發送訂單確認時成立。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>支付安全</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們採用業界標準的加密技術（如 SSL/TLS）保護支付過程中的資料傳輸安全。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您的支付細節資料（如完整信用卡號碼）將由通過認證的第三方支付服務提供商處理與儲存，我們不會儲存此類敏感資訊。我們僅儲存為履行合同所必需的部分資訊（如交易授權碼、掩碼後的卡號）。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>付款爭議、退款與撤銷權</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您對某筆支付交易有疑問或爭議，請於交易發生後&nbsp;<strong>14 日內</strong>&nbsp;聯繫我們的客服。我們將依據《奧地利民法典》及支付服務提供商的規則進行調查。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若因可歸責於我們的系統錯誤導致重複扣款或錯誤扣款，我們將在核實後&nbsp;<strong>14 個工作日內</strong>&nbsp;啟動退款程序。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">根據歐盟及奧地利消費者保護法規，若您作為消費者通過遠距簽訂合同，通常享有&nbsp;<strong>14 天</strong>&nbsp;的無需理由的撤銷權。具體退款及撤銷政策將在您購買具體服務前明確告知，並構成合同的一部分。部分服務（如即時提供的數位內容，且您已同意放棄撤銷權）可能不適用此規定。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>價格、稅金與費用</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本應用程式內顯示的價格均以&nbsp;<strong>歐元</strong>&nbsp;或明確標示的當地貨幣為準。根據《奧地利稅法》，所有顯示給奧地利境內消費者的價格必須包含適用的增值稅。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">實際扣款金額以最終支付頁面顯示的總金額（含稅）為準。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您使用外幣支付，可能因發卡行或支付平台適用的匯率而產生金額差異，此風險由您自行承擔。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>六、 智慧財產權</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本應用程式內的所有內容，包括但不限於軟體、程式碼、資料庫、文字、圖片、圖形、商標及介面設計，均受奧地利及國際著作權法、商標法及其他智慧財產權法律保護，其權利歸屬於我們或我們的授權方。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">未經我們明確書面授權，您不得為任何商業或非商業目的，複製、修改、改編、轉載、發布、反向工程、創建衍生作品或利用本應用程式的任何部分。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>七、 責任限制與免責聲明</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本應用程式及其服務僅依「現狀」及「現有」基礎提供。在法律允許的範圍內，我們不對服務的及時性、不中斷性、安全性或無錯誤作出任何明示或默示的保證。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">對於因不可抗力（如戰爭、自然災害、政府管制、網絡通訊故障等）或非因我們過錯導致的第三方行為（如黑客攻擊）所造成的服務中斷、資料遺失或任何其他損失，我們不承擔責任。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們的賠償責任，無論基於何種法律原因，僅限於可預見的、典型的合同損害。對於輕微過失違反非主要合同義務的情況，我們不承擔責任。此責任限制不適用於人身傷害、對生命、身體或健康的損害，以及根據《奧地利產品責任法》應承擔的強制性責任。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>八、 適用法律與管轄</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本協議之解釋與適用，以及因本協議產生之一切法律關係，均應以&nbsp;<strong>奧地利共和國法律</strong>&nbsp;為準據法，但不適用其衝突法規則。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\">若因本協議產生任何爭議，雙方應首先致力於友好協商解決。若協商不成，</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您作為消費者，且您的常住地在奧地利，您可以向您所在地的管轄法院提起訴訟，也可以向我們所在地的法院提起。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您非消費者，雙方同意以&nbsp;<strong>奧地利薩爾茨堡地方法院</strong>&nbsp;為第一審管轄法院。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您同意，在訴諸司法程序前，可考慮透過奧歐盟的線上爭議解決平台尋求解決。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>九、 其他規定</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本協議中任何條款被認定為無效或不可執行，不影響其他條款的有效性與可執行性。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們未行使本協議項下的任何權利，不構成對該權利的放棄。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>十、 聯繫我們</strong><br />若您對本協議、網絡支付或您的資料有任何疑問，請透過以下方式聯繫我們：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">客服郵箱：support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">官方網站：<a style=\"color: var(--dsw-alias-brand-text); transition: box-shadow var(--ds-transition-duration)var(--ds-ease-in-out); border-left: 3px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-right: 3px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-top: 2px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; text-decoration: none; position: relative;\" href=\"https://www.lumoguide.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.lumoguide.com</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">感謝您使用 Lumo Guide！</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">English Vision：</p>\r\n<h1 data-path-to-node=\"2\">Lumo Guide App VIP Membership Service Payment Agreement</h1>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong>Effective Date:</strong>&nbsp;October 1, 2025</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong>Last Updated:</strong>&nbsp;October 1, 2025</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Welcome to&nbsp;<strong>Lumo Guide</strong>&nbsp;(hereinafter referred to as \"the App\"). This Agreement is a legally binding agreement between you (hereinafter referred to as \"the User\") and the operator of the App. Please read this Agreement carefully, as it describes how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal data, and explicitly stipulates the rights and obligations of both parties, particularly regarding online payments.&nbsp;<strong>If you do not agree to any part of this Agreement, please stop using the App immediately.</strong></p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"6\">I. Acceptance and Amendment of the Agreement</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">By downloading, installing, registering, accessing, or using the App, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to be bound by all terms and conditions of this Agreement and undertake to comply with all applicable laws and regulations.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\">We reserve the right to unilaterally modify this Agreement as necessary for business development or to comply with the legal requirements of Austria and the European Union. The modified Agreement will be published within the App with the \"Last Updated\" date indicated. Your continued use of the App after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the revised Agreement. For material changes, we will make reasonable efforts to provide more explicit notification.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"9\">II. Account Registration and Usage</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"10\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\">You must provide true, accurate, current, and complete information for registration and are obligated to update such information promptly.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\">You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password and shall bear legal responsibility for all activities occurring under your account. You must notify us immediately upon discovery of any unauthorized use of your account.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\">You shall not use the App for any illegal, infringing, or unethical purposes. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account immediately and pursue legal remedies for such violations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"11\">III. Privacy and Data Protection</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"12\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\">We will collect, process, use, and protect your personal data legally, reasonably, and necessarily in accordance with our separate&nbsp;<em>Privacy Policy</em>, the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Data Protection Act (DSG)</em>, and the EU&nbsp;<em>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</em>. The&nbsp;<em>Privacy Policy</em>&nbsp;constitutes an integral part of this Agreement.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\">Data we may collect includes, but is not limited to: name, email address, location information, device identifiers, payment-related information, and service usage records.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\">Regarding your data subject rights (such as access, rectification, erasure, restriction of processing, data portability, and the right to object), please refer to our&nbsp;<em>Privacy Policy</em>&nbsp;and submit requests through the designated contact methods.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"13\">IV. Scope of Services</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"14\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\">Lumo Guide provides tour guides, route planning, attraction recommendations, and related value-added services (collectively, \"the Services\").</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\">We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate all or part of the Services at any time without individual notice. Where required by law, we will provide advance notice for significant changes or termination of services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"15\">V. Online Payment Terms</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong>1. Payment Methods</strong>&nbsp;The App supports the following payment methods:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"17\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\">Credit/Debit Cards</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\">Third-party payment platforms (e.g., Apple Pay, Google Pay, PayPal, etc.)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,2,0\">Other payment methods as announced by the App.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong>2. Payment Authorization and Contract Formation</strong>&nbsp;By initiating a payment transaction, you are making a binding offer and authorizing us or our partner third-party payment service providers to deduct the corresponding amount from your designated payment method. The contract is formed when we unconditionally accept your offer and send an order confirmation via the system or email.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>3. Payment Security</strong>&nbsp;We employ industry-standard encryption technologies (such as SSL/TLS) to protect data transmission during the payment process. Your sensitive payment details (such as full credit card numbers) are processed and stored by certified third-party payment service providers; we do not store such sensitive information. We only store information necessary for contract fulfillment (e.g., transaction authorization codes, masked card numbers).</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong>4. Payment Disputes, Refunds, and Right of Withdrawal</strong>&nbsp;* If you have questions or disputes regarding a transaction, please contact our customer service within&nbsp;<strong>14 days</strong>&nbsp;of the transaction. We will investigate in accordance with the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Civil Code (ABGB)</em>&nbsp;and the rules of the payment service provider.</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"21\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\">In the event of duplicate or erroneous charges attributable to our system errors, we will initiate a refund process within&nbsp;<strong>14 working days</strong>&nbsp;after verification.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21,1,0\">Pursuant to EU and Austrian consumer protection regulations, if you enter into a contract as a consumer via distance communication, you generally enjoy a&nbsp;<strong>14-day right of withdrawal</strong>&nbsp;without providing reasons. Specific refund and withdrawal policies will be clearly communicated before your purchase and form part of the contract. Certain services (e.g., digital content provided immediately where you have agreed to waive your right of withdrawal) may be exempt from this provision.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong>5. Pricing, Taxes, and Fees</strong>&nbsp;Prices displayed in the App are in&nbsp;<strong>Euros (EUR)</strong>&nbsp;or clearly marked local currencies. Pursuant to the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Tax Act</em>, all prices displayed to consumers within Austria must include applicable Value Added Tax (VAT). The actual amount charged is the total amount (including tax) shown on the final payment page. If you pay in a foreign currency, you bear the risk of currency fluctuations or exchange fees applied by your issuing bank or payment platform.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\">VI. Intellectual Property Rights</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\">All content within the App, including but not limited to software, code, databases, text, images, graphics, trademarks, and interface designs, is protected by Austrian and international copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws. All rights belong to us or our licensors. Without our express written authorization, you may not copy, modify, adapt, reproduce, publish, reverse engineer, create derivative works from, or exploit any part of the App for any commercial or non-commercial purposes.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\">VII. Limitation of Liability and Disclaimer</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"26\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,0,0\">The App and its services are provided on an \"as is\" and \"as available\" basis. To the extent permitted by law, we make no express or implied warranties regarding the timeliness, uninterrupted nature, security, or error-free status of the services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\">We shall not be liable for service interruptions, data loss, or any other losses caused by Force Majeure (e.g., war, natural disasters, government regulations, network failures) or third-party actions (e.g., hacking) not resulting from our fault.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\">Our liability, regardless of the legal basis, is limited to foreseeable, typical contractual damages. We are not liable for slight negligence in breaching non-essential contractual obligations. This limitation does not apply to personal injury, damage to life, limb, or health, or mandatory liability under the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Product Liability Act</em>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\">VIII. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"28\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,0,0\">The interpretation and application of this Agreement, as well as all legal relationships arising therefrom, shall be governed by the laws of the&nbsp;<strong>Republic of Austria</strong>, excluding its conflict of law rules.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,1,0\">Any disputes arising from this Agreement shall first be settled through friendly negotiation. If negotiation fails:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"28,1,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,1,1,0,0\">If you are a consumer residing in Austria, you may bring an action in the court of your place of residence or in the court of our place of business.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,1,1,1,0\">If you are not a consumer, both parties agree that the&nbsp;<strong>Regional Court of Salzburg, Austria</strong>, shall have exclusive jurisdiction as the court of first instance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28,2,0\">You agree that prior to litigation, resolution may be sought through the European Union\'s Online Dispute Resolution (ODR) platform.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"29\">IX. Miscellaneous Provisions</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"30\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,0,0\">If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the validity and enforceability of the remaining provisions shall not be affected.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30,1,0\">Our failure to exercise any right under this Agreement does not constitute a waiver of such right.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"31\">X. Contact Us</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\">If you have any questions regarding this Agreement, online payments, or your data, please contact us via:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"33\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\"><strong>Customer Service Email:</strong>&nbsp;support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\"><strong>Official Website:</strong>&nbsp;<a class=\"ng-star-inserted\" href=\"https://www.lumoguide.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-hveid=\"0\" data-ved=\"0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwjuyK3n8byRAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ2AE\">https://www.lumoguide.com</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">Thank you for using Lumo Guide!</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">简体字版本：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">路盟 Lumo Guide 应用程式 VIP 会员服务付款协议</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">生效日期：2025年10月1日</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">最后更新日期：2025年10月1日</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">欢迎使用 路盟 Lumo Guide（以下称「本应用程式」）。本协议是您（以下称「用户」）与本应用程式营运者之间具有法律约束力的协议。请仔细阅读本协议，其说明了我们如何收集、使用、储存及保护您的个人资料，并明确规定了双方，特别是关于网络支付的权利与义务。若您不同意本协议的任何内容，请立即停止使用本应用程式。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">一、 协议的接受与修改</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">当您下载、安装、注册、存取或使用本应用程式时，即表示您已阅读、理解、并同意接受本协议的所有条款与条件，并承诺遵守所有适用的法律与法规。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们有权根据业务发展需要或为符合奥地利及欧盟法律要求而单方面修改本协议。修改后的协议将于本应用程式内公布更新版本，并注明最后更新日期。若您于协议修改后继续使用本应用程式，即视为接受修改后的协议。对于重大变更，我们将尽合理努力提供更明确的通知。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">二、 帐号注册与使用</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">您需提供真实、准确、最新及完整的资料进行注册，并有义务及时更新此等资料。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">您须对您的帐号及密码负有保密责任，并对在您帐号下发生的所有活动承担法律责任。一旦发现任何未经授权使用您帐号的情况，应立即通知我们。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">您不得利用本应用程式从事任何非法、侵权或违反公序良俗的行为，否则我们有权立即暂停或终止您的帐号，并保留追究法律责任的权利。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">三、 隐私权与资料保护</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们将依照单独的《隐私权政策》以及《奥地利资料保护法》和欧盟《通用资料保护条例》的规定，合法、合理、必要地收集、处理、使用及保护您的个人资料。该《隐私权政策》为本协议不可分割的一部分。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们可能收集的资料包括但不限于：姓名、电子邮件地址、位置资讯、装置识别码、支付相关资讯及服务使用纪录。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">关于您的资料主体权利（如存取、更正、删除、限制处理、资料可携性及反对权），请参阅我们的《隐私权政策》并透过指定联络方式提出请求。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">四、 服务内容</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">Lumo Guide 提供导览、路线规划、景点推荐及相关增值服务（以下统称「本服务」）。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们保留随时修改、暂停或终止部分或全部服务的权利，恕不另行个别通知。若法律要求，对于服务的重大变更或终止，我们将提供提前通知。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">五、 网络支付条款</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">支付方式</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本应用程式支援以下支付方式：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">信用卡/借记卡</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">第三方支付平台（如：Apple Pay、Google Pay、PayPal等）</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">其他本应用程式另行公告之支付方式。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">支付授权与合同成立</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">当您进行支付操作时，即表示您发出具有约束力的要约，授权我们或我们合作的第三方支付服务提供商从您指定的支付方式中扣除相应款项。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">合同在我们无条件接受您的要约并透过系统或电邮发送订单确认时成立。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">支付安全</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们采用业界标准的加密技术（如 SSL/TLS）保护支付过程中的资料传输安全。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">您的支付细节资料（如完整信用卡号码）将由通过认证的第三方支付服务提供商处理与储存，我们不会储存此类敏感资讯。我们仅储存为履行合同所必需的部分资讯（如交易授权码、掩码后的卡号）。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">付款争议、退款与撤销权</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若您对某笔支付交易有疑问或争议，请于交易发生后 14 日内 联系我们的客服。我们将依据《奥地利民法典》及支付服务提供商的规则进行调查。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若因可归责于我们的系统错误导致重复扣款或错误扣款，我们将在核实后 14 个工作日内 启动退款程序。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">根据欧盟及奥地利消费者保护法规，若您作为消费者通过远距签订合同，通常享有 14 天 的无需理由的撤销权。具体退款及撤销政策将在您购买具体服务前明确告知，并构成合同的一部分。部分服务（如即时提供的数位内容，且您已同意放弃撤销权）可能不适用此规定。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">价格、税金与费用</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本应用程式内显示的价格均以 欧元 或明确标示的当地货币为准。根据《奥地利税法》，所有显示给奥地利境内消费者的价格必须包含适用的增值税。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">实际扣款金额以最终支付页面显示的总金额（含税）为准。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若您使用外币支付，可能因发卡行或支付平台适用的汇率而产生金额差异，此风险由您自行承担。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">六、 智慧财产</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本应用程式内的所有内容，包括但不限于软体、程式码、资料库、文字、图片、图形、商标及介面设计，均受奥地利及国际著作权法、商标法及其他智慧财产权法律保护，其权利归属于我们或我们的授权方。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">未经我们明确书面授权，您不得为任何商业或非商业目的，复制、修改、改编、转载、发布、反向工程、创建衍生作品或利用本应用程式的任何部分。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">七、 责任限制与免责声明</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本应用程式及其服务仅依「现状」及「现有」基础提供。在法律允许的范围内，我们不对服务的及时性、不中断性、安全性或无错误作出任何明示或默示的保证。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">对于因不可抗力（如战争、自然灾害、政府管制、网络通讯故障等）或非因我们过错导致的第三方行为（如黑客攻击）所造成的服务中断、资料遗失或任何其他损失，我们不承担责任。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们的赔偿责任，无论基于何种法律原因，仅限于可预见的、典型的合同损害。对于轻微过失违反非主要合同义务的情况，我们不承担责任。此责任限制不适用于人身伤害、对生命、身体或健康的损害，以及根据《奥地利产品责任法》应承担的强制性责任。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">八、 适用法律与管辖</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本协议之解释与适用，以及因本协议产生之一切法律关系，均应以 奥地利共和国法律 为准据法，但不适用其冲突法规则。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若因本协议产生任何争议，双方应首先致力于友好协商解决。若协商不成，</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若您作为消费者，且您的常住地在奥地利，您可以向您所在地的管辖法院提起诉讼，也可以向我们所在地的法院提起。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若您非消费者，双方同意以 奥地利萨尔茨堡地方法院 为第一审管辖法院。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">您同意，在诉诸司法程序前，可考虑透过奥欧盟的线上争议解决平台寻求解决。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">九、 其他规定</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">本协议中任何条款被认定为无效或不可执行，不影响其他条款的有效性与可执行性。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">我们未行使本协议项下的任何权利，不构成对该权利的放弃。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">十、 联系我们</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">若您对本协议、网络支付或您的资料有任何疑问，请透过以下方式联系我们：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">客服邮箱：support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">官方网站：https://www.lumoguide.com</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\">感谢您使用 Lumo Guide！</p>','2025-09-13 09:24:30','2025-12-21 02:59:01'),(12,'VIP會員訂閱服務協議',2,'vip_user_subscribe','<h3 style=\"font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; margin: 32px 0px 16px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115;\"><span style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">路盟 Lumo Guide VIP 會員訂閱服務協議</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>生效日期：2025年10月1日</strong><br /><strong>最後更新日期：2025年10月1日</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">歡迎訂閱 路盟 Lumo Guide VIP 會員服務（以下稱「本服務」）。本協議是您（以下稱「用戶」或「訂閱者」）與本應用程式營運者之間關於VIP會員訂閱服務的具有法律約束力的協議。請仔細閱讀本協議，其說明了與您訂閱相關的權利、義務、付款條款以及個人資料處理方式。若您不同意本協議的任何內容，請立即停止訂閱程序。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>一、 協議的接受與修改</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">當您啟動VIP會員訂閱程序、完成支付或開始使用本服務時，即表示您已閱讀、理解、並同意接受本協議的所有條款與條件，並承諾遵守所有適用的奧地利及歐盟法律與法規。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們有權根據業務發展需要或為符合奧地利及歐盟法律要求而單方面修改本協議。對於涉及收費、自動續訂、取消政策等重大權益的變更，我們將於本應用程式內公布更新版本，並透過電子郵件或應用程式內通知等合理方式提醒您。若您於協議修改生效後繼續使用本服務，即視為接受修改後的協議。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>二、 帳號與資格</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您需擁有有效的Lumo Guide帳號方可訂閱本服務。您應提供真實、準確、最新及完整的資料，並對您帳號下的所有活動承擔法律責任。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本服務僅供個人、非商業用途使用。您不得轉讓、出借或分享您的VIP會員資格予任何第三方。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>三、 隱私權與資料保護</strong><br />我們將依照單獨的《隱私權政策》以及《奧地利資料保護法》和歐盟《通用資料保護條例》的規定，處理您為訂閱和使用本服務而提供的個人資料。該《隱私權政策》為本協議不可分割的一部分。</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>四、 VIP會員服務內容與分級權益</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>服務權益</strong>：VIP會員享有其訂閱等級對應的專屬權益，具體分級與權益如下：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>Regular 會員</strong>：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">可添加一個展示店鋪。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">在線即時聊天功能。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">在線預訂及預約管理功能。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">城市內容中的推薦為期三天。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">積分兌換功能。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">邀請好友持續累積積分。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>Gold 會員</strong>：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">享有 Regular 會員所有功能與權限。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">可添加同類型下多個商鋪。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">城市內容中的推薦二十天。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">平台內首頁列表推薦五天。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">店鋪展示功能。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>Diamond 會員</strong>：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">享有 Gold 會員所有功能與權限。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">可添加不同類型下多個商鋪。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">平台內首頁大圖輪播推薦五天。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">平台內首頁大圖輪播推薦後再列表推薦十五天。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>推薦服務說明</strong>：所有「推薦」服務（包括但不限於城市內容推薦、首頁列表推薦、首頁大圖輪播推薦）的具體展示位置、時長與效果，由平台根據運營策略進行安排。我們承諾在約定周期內盡商業上的合理努力進行展示，但不對推薦的點擊量、轉化率或具體展示位置作任何保證。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>服務變更與中止</strong>：我們保留隨時修改、新增或刪除部分VIP權益的權利，但此類變更不會實質性減損您當前訂閱周期內已支付對價的核心權益。若因不可抗力或無法歸責於我們的原因導致服務中止，我們將盡力恢復，但不承擔相應責任。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>五、 訂閱與付款條款</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>訂閱類型</strong>：本服務提供不同周期的訂閱方案（如月費、年費等）。具體方案與價格將在您訂閱前明確展示。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>自動續訂與扣款</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">除非您在當前訂閱周期結束前關閉自動續訂功能，否則您的訂閱將<strong>自動續訂</strong>。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您授權我們在每個訂閱周期結束前（約24小時內）透過您綁定的支付方式自動扣除下一周期的費用。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">關閉自動續訂的具體路徑為：應用程式內【帳戶設定】-&gt;【訂閱管理】。關閉後，服務將在已付費周期的期末終止。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>免費試用期</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們可能提供附帶&nbsp;<strong>30 天</strong>免費試用期的訂閱方案。<strong>在試用期結束前，您將收到通知</strong>。若您未在試用期結束前取消訂閱，系統將自動從您綁定的支付方式扣除第一期費用，並開始正式訂閱。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">每位用戶僅享有一次免費試用資格。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>價格調整</strong>：我們保留因應營運成本變化而調整訂閱價格的權利。價格調整將於<strong>續訂周期生效</strong>。我們將在價格調整前，透過電子郵件或應用程式內顯著方式提前<strong>30天</strong>通知您。若您不同意新的價格，您應在當前周期結束前關閉自動續訂。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>支付安全與方式</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們採用業界標準的加密技術（如 SSL/TLS）保護支付過程中的資料傳輸安全。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您的支付細節資料由通過認證的第三方支付服務提供商處理，我們不會儲存完整信用卡號等敏感資訊。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>付款爭議</strong>：若您對扣款有疑問，請於交易發生後<strong>14日內</strong>聯繫客服。若因可歸責於我們的系統錯誤導致重複扣款，我們將在核實後<strong>14個工作日內</strong>啟動退款。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>六、 取消、退款與撤銷權</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>取消訂閱</strong>：您可隨時透過關閉「自動續訂」功能來取消未來的訂閱，此操作不會觸發當期已付費用的退款。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\"><strong>撤銷權</strong>：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">根據歐盟及奧地利消費者保護法，若您作為消費者通過遠距簽訂合同，通常享有<strong>14天</strong>的無需理由的撤銷權。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>重要例外</strong>：若您在本協議生效後立即同意我們開始提供服務（例如即時開通VIP權限），並在確認訂閱時知悉並同意此條款，則您同意，一旦您開始使用本服務或14天撤銷期屆滿，即<strong>喪失您的撤銷權</strong>，且您無權就已完成提供的服務要求部分退款。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您在14天撤銷期內未使用任何本服務，您仍有權行使撤銷權並獲得全額退款。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\"><strong>因故退款</strong>：除上述法律規定的撤銷權情況外，所有訂閱費用一經支付，原則上不予退款。若因本應用程式方面的重大故障導致服務長期完全無法使用，我們將根據具體情況本著公平原則處理。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>七、 智慧財產權與用戶內容</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本應用程式及VIP服務內的所有內容，包括獨家導覽、軟體、商標等，均受奧地利及國際智慧財產權法律保護。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您通過本服務添加、展示的店鋪、內容或資訊，您應保證其擁有合法權利，且不侵犯任何第三方的智慧財產權或合法權益。您在此授予我們為提供本服務之目的而在全球範圍內使用、展示、推廣該等內容的免費許可。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>八、 責任限制與免責聲明</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本服務僅依「現狀」及「現有」基礎提供。我們不保證服務不中斷或完全無錯誤，尤其不保證第四條所述的「推薦」服務能帶來任何特定的商業效果。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">我們的賠償責任，僅限於可預見的、典型的合同損害。對於輕微過失違反非主要合同義務的情況，我們不承擔責任。此責任限制不適用於人身傷害、對生命、身體或健康的損害，以及根據《奧地利產品責任法》應承擔的強制性責任。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>九、 適用法律與管轄</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\" start=\"1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">本協議之解釋與適用，以及因本協議產生之一切法律關係，均應以<strong>奧地利共和國法律</strong>為準據法，但不適用其衝突法規則。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 8px 0px;\">若因本協議產生任何爭議，雙方應首先友好協商解決。若協商不成，</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您作為消費者，且您的常住地在奧地利，您可以向您所在地的管轄法院提起訴訟。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">若您非消費者，雙方同意以<strong>奧地利薩爾茨堡地方法院</strong>為第一審管轄法院。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">您同意，在訴諸司法程序前，可考慮透過歐盟的線上爭議解決平台尋求解決。</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\"><strong>十、 聯繫我們</strong><br />若您對本訂閱協議有任何疑問，請透過以下方式聯繫我們：</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">客服郵箱：support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin-top: 6px;\">\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px !important 0px 0px 0px;\">官方網站：<a style=\"color: var(--dsw-alias-brand-text); transition: box-shadow var(--ds-transition-duration)var(--ds-ease-in-out); border-left: 3px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-right: 3px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-top: 2px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(var(--ds-rgba-transparent)); margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; text-decoration: none; position: relative;\" href=\"https://www.lumoguide.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.lumoguide.com</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">感謝您訂閱 Lumo Guide VIP 服務！</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0px; caret-color: #0f1115; color: #0f1115; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;\">English Vision：</p>\r\n<h1 data-path-to-node=\"2\">Lumo Guide VIP Membership Subscription Service Agreement</h1>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong>Effective Date:</strong>&nbsp;October 1, 2025</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong>Last Updated:</strong>&nbsp;October 1, 2025</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Welcome to the&nbsp;<strong>Lumo Guide VIP Membership Service</strong>&nbsp;(hereinafter referred to as \"the Service\"). This Agreement is a legally binding agreement between you (hereinafter referred to as \"the User\" or \"the Subscriber\") and the operator of the App regarding the VIP membership subscription service. Please read this Agreement carefully, as it outlines your rights and obligations related to the subscription, payment terms, and the processing of personal data.&nbsp;<strong>If you do not agree to any part of this Agreement, please stop the subscription process immediately.</strong></p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"6\">I. Acceptance and Amendment of the Agreement</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"7\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\">By initiating the VIP membership subscription process, completing payment, or starting to use the Service, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to be bound by all terms and conditions of this Agreement and undertake to comply with all applicable Austrian and European Union laws and regulations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\">We reserve the right to unilaterally modify this Agreement based on business development needs or to comply with the legal requirements of Austria and the EU. For material changes involving fees, auto-renewal, or cancellation policies, we will publish the updated version within the App and notify you through reasonable means such as email or in-app notifications. Your continued use of the Service after such modifications take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised Agreement.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\">II. Account and Eligibility</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"9\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\">You must possess a valid Lumo Guide account to subscribe to the Service. You shall provide true, accurate, current, and complete information and bear legal responsibility for all activities under your account.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\">The Service is provided for personal, non-commercial use only. You may not transfer, lend, or share your VIP membership status with any third party.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"10\">III. Privacy and Data Protection</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\">We will process the personal data you provide for subscribing to and using the Service in accordance with our separate&nbsp;<em>Privacy Policy</em>, the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Data Protection Act (DSG)</em>, and the EU&nbsp;<em>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</em>. The&nbsp;<em>Privacy Policy</em>&nbsp;constitutes an integral part of this Agreement.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"12\">IV. VIP Membership Service Content and Tiered Benefits</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong>1. Service Benefits:</strong>&nbsp;VIP members enjoy exclusive benefits corresponding to their subscription tier as follows:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"14\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\"><strong>Regular Member:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,0,0\">Add one display store.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,1,0\">Real-time online chat functionality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,2,0\">Online booking and reservation management functionality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,3,0\">Three-day recommendation within city content.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,4,0\">Points redemption functionality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,1,5,0\">Invite friends to accumulate points continuously.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\"><strong>Gold Member:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1,0,0\">Includes all features and permissions of a Regular Member.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1,1,0\">Add multiple stores under the same business type.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1,2,0\">Twenty-day recommendation within city content.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1,3,0\">Five-day homepage list recommendation within the platform.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,1,4,0\">Enhanced store display functionality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,0\"><strong>Diamond Member:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"14,2,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,1,0,0\">Includes all features and permissions of a Gold Member.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,1,1,0\">Add multiple stores under different business types.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,1,2,0\">Five-day homepage large banner carousel recommendation.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,2,1,3,0\">Fifteen-day homepage list recommendation following the banner carousel period.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong>2. Description of Recommendation Services:</strong>&nbsp;The specific display position, duration, and effect of all \"Recommendation\" services (including but not limited to city content, homepage lists, and banner carousels) are arranged by the platform according to its operational strategy. We undertake to use commercially reasonable efforts for display during the agreed period but do&nbsp;<strong>not</strong>&nbsp;guarantee click-through rates, conversion rates, or specific display positions.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong>3. Service Modification and Suspension:</strong>&nbsp;We reserve the right to modify, add, or delete certain VIP benefits at any time. However, such changes will not substantially diminish the core benefits for which you have already paid in your current subscription cycle. We are not liable for service interruptions caused by Force Majeure or reasons beyond our control, though we will endeavor to restore service.</p>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"17\">V. Subscription and Payment Terms</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"18\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,0,0\"><strong>Subscription Types:</strong>&nbsp;The Service offers various subscription plans (e.g., monthly, annual). Specific plans and prices will be clearly displayed before you subscribe.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,1,0\"><strong>Auto-Renewal and Billing:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"18,1,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,1,1,0,0\">Your subscription will automatically renew unless you disable the auto-renewal feature before the end of the current cycle.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,1,1,1,0\">You authorize us to automatically deduct the fee for the next cycle from your bound payment method within approximately 24 hours before the end of each subscription cycle.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,1,1,2,0\">The path to disable auto-renewal is:&nbsp;<strong>[Account Settings] -&gt; [Subscription Management]</strong>&nbsp;within the App. After disabling, the service will terminate at the end of the paid cycle.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,2,0\"><strong>Free Trial Period:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"18,2,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,2,1,0,0\">We may offer subscription plans with a&nbsp;<strong>30-day free trial</strong>. You will be notified before the trial ends. If you do not cancel before the end of the trial, the system will automatically charge the first cycle\'s fee and start the formal subscription.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,2,1,1,0\">Each user is entitled to only one free trial.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,3,0\"><strong>Price Adjustments:</strong>&nbsp;We reserve the right to adjust subscription prices due to changes in operating costs. Price adjustments will take effect in the next renewal cycle. We will notify you at least 30 days in advance via email or prominent in-app notices. If you disagree with the new price, you must disable auto-renewal before the current cycle ends.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,4,0\"><strong>Payment Security:</strong>&nbsp;We employ industry-standard encryption (SSL/TLS) to protect data transmission. Your sensitive payment details are processed by certified third-party providers; we do not store full credit card numbers.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18,5,0\"><strong>Payment Disputes:</strong>&nbsp;For queries regarding charges, please contact customer service within 14 days of the transaction. For duplicate charges due to our system errors, we will initiate a refund within 14 working days after verification.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"19\">VI. Cancellation, Refund, and Right of Withdrawal</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"20\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,0,0\"><strong>Cancellation:</strong>&nbsp;You may cancel future subscriptions at any time by disabling \"Auto-Renewal.\" This action does not trigger a refund for the current paid cycle.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,1,0\"><strong>Right of Withdrawal:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"20,1,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,1,1,0,0\">Pursuant to EU and Austrian consumer protection laws, consumers entering into a distance contract generally enjoy a&nbsp;<strong>14-day right of withdrawal</strong>&nbsp;without reason.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,1,1,1,0\"><strong>Important Exception:</strong>&nbsp;If you agree that we begin providing the Service immediately upon the commencement of this Agreement (e.g., instant activation of VIP privileges) and acknowledge this at the time of subscription, you agree that you&nbsp;<strong>lose your right of withdrawal</strong>&nbsp;once the Service has begun or after the 14-day period expires. You are not entitled to a partial refund for services already provided.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,1,1,2,0\">If you have not used any part of the Service within the 14-day withdrawal period, you retain the right to exercise withdrawal and receive a full refund.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20,2,0\"><strong>General Refund Policy:</strong>&nbsp;Except for the legal withdrawal rights mentioned above, all subscription fees are non-refundable once paid. In cases of major App failures resulting in long-term total unavailability of the Service, we will handle requests based on the principle of fairness.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"21\">VII. Intellectual Property and User Content</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"22\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22,0,0\">All content within the App and VIP Service (exclusive guides, software, trademarks, etc.) is protected by Austrian and international intellectual property laws.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22,1,0\">Regarding the stores, content, or information you add or display through the Service, you warrant that you possess the legal rights and do not infringe on any third party\'s rights. You hereby grant us a royalty-free, worldwide license to use, display, and promote such content for the purpose of providing the Service.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\">VIII. Limitation of Liability and Disclaimer</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"24\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24,0,0\">The Service is provided on an \"as is\" and \"as available\" basis. We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free service, specifically regarding the commercial effectiveness of the \"Recommendation\" services described in Section IV.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24,1,0\">Our liability is limited to foreseeable, typical contractual damages. We are not liable for slight negligence in breaching non-essential obligations. This does not apply to personal injury, damage to life, limb, or health, or mandatory liability under the&nbsp;<em>Austrian Product Liability Act</em>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\">IX. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"26\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,0,0\">The interpretation and application of this Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the&nbsp;<strong>Republic of Austria</strong>, excluding its conflict of law rules.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,0\">Disputes shall first be settled through friendly negotiation. If negotiation fails:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,0,0\">Consumers residing in Austria may file suit in their local competent court.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,1,1,1,0\">Non-consumers agree that the&nbsp;<strong>Regional Court of Salzburg, Austria</strong>, shall have exclusive jurisdiction as the court of first instance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26,2,0\">Users may consider seeking resolution through the EU\'s Online Dispute Resolution (ODR) platform before pursuing judicial proceedings.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"27\">X. Contact Us</h3>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\">If you have questions regarding this Subscription Agreement, please contact us via:</p>\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><strong>Customer Service Email:</strong>&nbsp;support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><strong>Official Website:</strong>&nbsp;<a class=\"ng-star-inserted\" href=\"https://www.lumoguide.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-hveid=\"0\" data-ved=\"0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwjuyK3n8byRAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ6gE\">https://www.lumoguide.com</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Thank you for subscribing to Lumo Guide VIP services!</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">简体字版本：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-path-to-node=\"30\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>路盟 Lumo Guide VIP 会员订阅服务协议</strong></span></p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">生效日期：2025年10月1日</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">最后更新日期：2025年10月1日</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">欢迎订阅 路盟 Lumo Guide VIP 会员服务（以下称「本服务」）。本协议是您（以下称「用户」或「订阅者」）与本应用程式营运者之间关于VIP会员订阅服务的具有法律约束力的协议。请仔细阅读本协议，其说明了与您订阅相关的权利、义务、付款条款以及个人资料处理方式。若您不同意本协议的任何内容，请立即停止订阅程序。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">一、 协议的接受与修改</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">当您启动VIP会员订阅程序、完成支付或开始使用本服务时，即表示您已阅读、理解、并同意接受本协议的所有条款与条件，并承诺遵守所有适用的奥地利及欧盟法律与法规。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">我们有权根据业务发展需要或为符合奥地利及欧盟法律要求而单方面修改本协议。对于涉及收费、自动续订、取消政策等重大权益的变更，我们将于本应用程式内公布更新版本，并透过电子邮件或应用程式内通知等合理方式提醒您。若您于协议修改生效后继续使用本服务，即视为接受修改后的协议。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">二、 帐号与资格</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">您需拥有有效的Lumo Guide帐号方可订阅本服务。您应提供真实、准确、最新及完整的资料，并对您帐号下的所有活动承担法律责任。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">本服务仅供个人、非商业用途使用。您不得转让、出借或分享您的VIP会员资格予任何第三方。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">三、 隐私权与资料保护</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">我们将依照单独的《隐私权政策》以及《奥地利资料保护法》和欧盟《通用资料保护条例》的规定，处理您为订阅和使用本服务而提供的个人资料。该《隐私权政策》为本协议不可分割的一部分。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">四、 VIP会员服务内容与分级权益</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">服务权益：VIP会员享有其订阅等级对应的专属权益，具体分级与权益如下：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Regular 会员：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">可添加一个展示店铺。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">在线即时聊天功能。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">在线预订及预约管理功能。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">城市内容中的推荐为期三天。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">积分兑换功能。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">邀请好友持续累积积分。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Gold 会员：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">享有 Regular 会员所有功能与权限。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">可添加同类型下多个商铺。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">城市内容中的推荐二十天。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">平台内首页列表推荐五天。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">店铺展示功能。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">Diamond 会员：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">享有 Gold 会员所有功能与权限。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">可添加不同类型下多个商铺。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">平台内首页大图轮播推荐五天。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">平台内首页大图轮播推荐后再列表推荐十五天。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">推荐服务说明：所有「推荐」服务（包括但不限于城市内容推荐、首页列表推荐、首页大图轮播推荐）的具体展示位置、时长与效果，由平台根据运营策略进行安排。我们承诺在约定周期内尽商业上的合理努力进行展示，但不对推荐的点击量、转化率或具体展示位置作任何保证。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">服务变更与中止：我们保留随时修改、新增或删除部分VIP权益的权利，但此类变更不会实质性减损您当前订阅周期内已支付对价的核心权益。若因不可抗力或无法归责于我们的原因导致服务中止，我们将尽力恢复，但不承担相应责任。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">五、 订阅与付款条款</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">订阅类型：本服务提供不同周期的订阅方案（如月费、年费等）。具体方案与价格将在您订阅前明确展示。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">自动续订与扣款</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">除非您在当前订阅周期结束前关闭自动续订功能，否则您的订阅将自动续订。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">您授权我们在每个订阅周期结束前（约24小时内）透过您绑定的支付方式自动扣除下一周期的费用。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">关闭自动续订的具体路径为：应用程式内【帐户设定】-&gt;【订阅管理】。关闭后，服务将在已付费周期的期末终止。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">免费试用期</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">我们可能提供附带 30 天免费试用期的订阅方案。在试用期结束前，您将收到通知。若您未在试用期结束前取消订阅，系统将自动从您绑定的支付方式扣除第一期费用，并开始正式订阅。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">每位用户仅享有一次免费试用资格。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">价格调整：我们保留因应营运成本变化而调整订阅价格的权利。价格调整将于续订周期生效。我们将在价格调整前，透过电子邮件或应用程式内显著方式提前30天通知您。若您不同意新的价格，您应在当前周期结束前关闭自动续订。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">支付安全与方式</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">我们采用业界标准的加密技术（如 SSL/TLS）保护支付过程中的资料传输安全。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">您的支付细节资料由通过认证的第三方支付服务提供商处理，我们不会储存完整信用卡号等敏感资讯。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">付款争议：若您对扣款有疑问，请于交易发生后14日内联系客服。若因可归责于我们的系统错误导致重复扣款，我们将在核实后14个工作日内启动退款。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">六、 取消、退款与撤销权</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">取消订阅：您可随时透过关闭「自动续订」功能来取消未来的订阅，此操作不会触发当期已付费用的退款。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">撤销权：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">根据欧盟及奥地利消费者保护法，若您作为消费者通过远距签订合同，通常享有14天的无需理由的撤销权。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">重要例外：若您在本协议生效后立即同意我们开始提供服务（例如即时开通VIP权限），并在确认订阅时知悉并同意此条款，则您同意，一旦您开始使用本服务或14天撤销期届满，即丧失您的撤销权，且您无权就已完成提供的服务要求部分退款。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">若您在14天撤销期内未使用任何本服务，您仍有权行使撤销权并获得全额退款。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">因故退款：除上述法律规定的撤销权情况外，所有订阅费用一经支付，原则上不予退款。若因本应用程式方面的重大故障导致服务长期完全无法使用，我们将根据具体情况本着公平原则处理。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">七、 智慧财产权与用户内容</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">本应用程式及VIP服务内的所有内容，包括独家导览、软体、商标等，均受奥地利及国际智慧财产权法律保护。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">您通过本服务添加、展示的店铺、内容或资讯，您应保证其拥有合法权利，且不侵犯任何第三方的智慧财产权或合法权益。您在此授予我们为提供本服务之目的而在全球范围内使用、展示、推广该等内容的免费许可。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">八、 责任限制与免责声明</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">本服务仅依「现状」及「现有」基础提供。我们不保证服务不中断或完全无错误，尤其不保证第四条所述的「推荐」服务能带来任何特定的商业效果。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">我们的赔偿责任，仅限于可预见的、典型的合同损害。对于轻微过失违反非主要合同义务的情况，我们不承担责任。此责任限制不适用于人身伤害、对生命、身体或健康的损害，以及根据《奥地利产品责任法》应承担的强制性责任。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">九、 适用法律与管辖</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">本协议之解释与适用，以及因本协议产生之一切法律关系，均应以奥地利共和国法律为准据法，但不适用其冲突法规则。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">若因本协议产生任何争议，双方应首先友好协商解决。若协商不成，</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">若您作为消费者，且您的常住地在奥地利，您可以向您所在地的管辖法院提起诉讼。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">若您非消费者，双方同意以奥地利萨尔茨堡地方法院为第一审管辖法院。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">您同意，在诉诸司法程序前，可考虑透过欧盟的线上争议解决平台寻求解决。</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">十、 联系我们</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">若您对本订阅协议有任何疑问，请透过以下方式联系我们：</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">客服邮箱：support@lumoguide.com</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">官方网站：https://www.lumoguide.com</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\">感谢您订阅 Lumo Guide VIP 服务！</p>','2025-09-13 09:25:14','2025-12-21 03:05:45'),(13,'系统logo',3,'system_logo','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/images/20251109/a9977dcf0e5459cdb73803c7060c7b1f.png','2025-10-29 18:42:25','2025-11-08 09:58:18'),(14,'系统Slogan',1,'system_slogan','路上有光，盟友相伴 - 路盟','2025-10-29 18:43:50','2025-10-29 18:43:50'),(15,'联系方式',1,'system_contact','support@lumoguide.com','2025-10-29 18:44:20','2026-01-15 00:40:14'),(16,'欢迎图-中文',3,'system_welcome_zh','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/images/20251109/d1739118baeac3fd86889fcad858809b.png','2025-10-29 19:18:49','2025-11-08 09:58:28'),(17,'欢迎图-英文',3,'system_welcome_en','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/images/20251109/1a60a5add69cd5e34e4f2f24612a319e.png','2025-10-29 19:19:10','2025-11-08 09:58:38'),(18,'出行方式',5,'transport_type','[\"\\u98de\\u673a\",\"\\u706b\\u8f66\",\"\\u9ad8\\u94c1\",\"\\u81ea\\u9a7e\"]','2026-04-01 20:26:20','2026-04-01 20:26:20');


